column4: hi guys, I need to open 7z files. However 8.10 hasnt native support for the format. I tried: sudo apt-get install p7zip but get the error: dpkg: syntax error: unknown group `postdrop' in statoverride file E: Sub-process /usr/bin/dpkg returned an error code (2)
you have any idea how to open z files?
you have any idea how to open 7z files?
